data.title: Citizen Snips
data.meta_description: "Less Than Hero" is the fourth episode episode in the  fourth season of the American animated television series Futurama, and the 58th episode of the series overall. It first aired on the Fox network in the United States on March 2, 2003. The episode was directed by Susie Dietter and written by Ron Weiner.
